<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Cookie Policy | Global Tip Calculator</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <style>
      body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(120deg, #38bdf8 0%, #34b3a0 60%, #a78bfa 100%);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      .cookie-card {
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 1.5em;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(52,179,160,0.13), 0 1.5px 8px rgba(52,179,160,0.07);
        padding: 2.5em 2em 2em 2em;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 3vh auto;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .cookie-card h1 {
        font-size: 2em;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #34b3a0;
        margin-bottom: 0.7em;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .cookie-card ul {
        padding-left: 1.2em;
        margin-bottom: 1.5em;
      }
      .cookie-card li {
        margin-bottom: 1em;
        font-size: 1.08em;
        color: #23272f;
      }
      .cookie-card p, .cookie-card a {
        font-size: 1.08em;
        color: #23272f;
        text-align: left;
      }
      .cookie-card a {
        color: #34b3a0;
        text-decoration: underline;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .cookie-card a:hover {
        color: #38bdf8;
      }
      @media (max-width: 700px) {
        .cookie-card {
          max-width: 98vw;
          padding: 1.2em 0.5em 1em 0.5em;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="cookie-card">
      <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p>At Global Tip Calculator, we use our own and third-party cookies to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Improve user experience and navigation.</li>
        <li>Show personalized ads through Google AdSense and other advertising partners.</li>
        <li>Analyze site traffic and usage to improve our services.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Cookies are small files stored on your device. You can configure your browser to reject them, but some features may not be available.</p>
      <p>By browsing this site, you accept the use of cookies. You can get more information or disable ad personalization in <a href="https://adssettings.google.com/authenticated" target="_blank">Google Ads Settings</a>.</p>
      <a href="/">Back to home</a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html> 